{"type": "article", "id": 22100, "title": "维持一些好奇心｜Daily Curiosity", "description": null, "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": null, "author": 3910, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/default_images/missing_article.png", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">你很可能已经无聊一周了。趁着最后一天激活一点好奇心，了解一些不太会注意到的小知识。</p>\n<p class=\"\">Daily Curiosity （<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/app/apple-store/id1000848816?pt=117495156&amp;ct=applandingdesktop&amp;mt=8\">iPhone</a>｜<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.curiosity.dailycuriosity&amp;referrer=utm_source%3Dcuriosity%26utm_medium%3Ddesktopapp%26utm_campaign%3Dlandinglogo\">Android</a>）每天会为你准备 5 条冷门知识。比如都说巧克力增肥，但黑巧克力含有大量黄酮，能够提升大脑的供血量。至于什么时候收到推送？你可以自己定。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606001921cBeNSsl8XaIDGMdi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">点击单条知识，还可以深入了解这些细节背后的故事和科学原理。当然，你还需要保持质疑的态度。所有信息也都提供了来源。</p>\n<p class=\"\">要是明天要早起上班打开的焦虑，还没有打败你。维持好奇心最好的办法，可能还是<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/19093.html\">看一些书</a>。</p>\n\n\n"}